<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Security Assessment Report</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f7f9fb;
            color: #222;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px 60px;
        }
        header {
            border-bottom: 3px solid #1a4a72;
            margin-bottom: 2em;
            padding-bottom: 1em;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #1a4a72;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin: 0;
        }
        h2, h3, h4 {
            color: #205080;
            margin-top: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 0.5em;
        }
        section {
            margin-bottom: 2em;
        }
        table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 1em 0;
            background: #fff;
        }
        th, td {
            border: 1px solid #b0c4de;
            padding: 10px 14px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        th {
            background: #e3ecf7;
        }
        code, pre {
            background: #f4f7fa;
            color: #333;
            font-family: "Fira Mono", "Consolas", monospace;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        blockquote {
            border-left: 4px solid #1a4a72;
            background: #f0f4fa;
            padding: 0.5em 1em;
            color: #555;
            margin: 1em 0;
        }
        ul, ol {
            margin-left: 2em;
        }
        .summary {
            background: #eaf3fa;
            border-left: 5px solid #1a4a72;
            padding: 1em;
            margin-bottom: 2em;
        }
        footer {
            margin-top: 3em;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #888;
            border-top: 1px solid #dbe6f3;
            padding-top: 1em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>[Insert Report Title]</h1>
        <div>Date: <span id="report-date">[Insert Date]</span></div>
        <div>Prepared by: <span id="report-author">[Insert Author]</span></div>
    </header>

    <section>
        <h2>1. Target Information</h2>
        <p>[Insert target information here]</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>2. Network Scans</h2>
        <p>[Include scan results here]</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>3. DNS Information</h2>
        <p>[Include DNS lookup results here]</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>4. Open Ports &amp; Detected Services</h2>
        <table>
            <tr>
                <th>Port</th>
                <th>Service</th>
                <th>Version</th>
            </tr>
            <!-- Insert rows here -->
        </table>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>5. Service-Specific Findings</h2>
        <p>[Describe findings for each detected service]</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>6. Security Recommendations</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>[Recommendation 1]</li>
            <li>[Recommendation 2]</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>7. Tool Recommendations</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>[Tool Recommendation 1]</li>
            <li>[Tool Recommendation 2]</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="summary">
        <h2>8. Summary / Executive Summary</h2>
        <p>[Provide a concise summary of the assessment and key findings]</p>
    </section>

    <footer>
        &copy; [DATETIME] Security Assessment Report &mdash; Confidential
    </footer>
</body>
</html>